body_html:
My guess is that your platform does support NEON but is falling in the default category: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/kernels/internal/BUILD#L363

To test that hypothesis, could you force it to use ":neon_tensor_utils" there?

My guess is that your platform does support NEON but is falling in the default category: https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/kernels/internal/BUILD#L363
